<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>for문 이용-크기별 출력</title>
</head>
<body>
	<h3> for문으로 10~35px크기 출력</h3>
	<hr>
	<script>
		for (var size=10; size<=35; size+=5) { //5씩 증가
			document.write("<span");
			document.write("style='font-size:"+size+ "px'>");
			document.write(size+"px");
			document.write("</span>");
		}
		</script>

</body>
</html>